True to the name and to its flavours, this Fresho Chettinad Gravy Mix is fiery, abundant with pepper and has the true mix of Chettinad spices that is hard to resist. Enjoy this thick, flavourful and piquant gravy either with meat cuts like chicken, mutton or beef or even experiment with your favourite cooked veggies like potatoes, beans, carrots and more. This gravy also tastes great with paneer, tofu or even soya chunks. Pair this dish with rice, roti or even appam. Explore a wide range of ready-to-cook, delicious Gravy Mixes from Fresho exclusively only Big Basket.

4. Prepare in just 10 minutes
